
COMPILER REQUIREMENTS AND EXECUTION INSTRUCTIONS
------------------------------------------------

REQUIREMENTS
------------
Python version 2.6.6 was used in development and testing (default on hpdc02).


RUNNING TEST
------------
By executing "make <WORKFLOW>", eg:

	make tfidf

Where "WORKFLOW" is the user's description of analytics query in JSON format, 
the compiler will generate Swan code, compile with c++ compiler, 
and run the workflow against the datasets specified in the users workflow
description.

Other examples:

	make kmeans
	make tfidf_and_kmeans             /* in-memory version */
	make tfidf_then_kmeans            /* file input/output version */
